  "detailed_description": "<h1>Bug Report</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/6b73d5d35aa263e32ea8b6b7906a5054.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you encounter any issues or bugs while playing the game, reporting them through 'Discord' allows for faster resolution.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can join 'Discord' via the link on the Steam store page.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Time To Usher In a Life As Ellie the Little Apprentice Witch!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of Ellie, a dispatched apprentice witch, and experience her journey of self development at Lucerine Ortu—a land of witches!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore brand-new areas, craft potions and help the villagers. A heartwarming and cozy adventure awaits you here.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish, gather, decorate your house, and interact with cats! We have all kinds of activities that will make every day an unforgettable experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/bb6a15ca90c666f515efdde60182dcd2.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/bb6a15ca90c666f515efdde60182dcd2.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/bb6a15ca90c666f515efdde60182dcd2.mp4?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/3512a31b9c028c09f86b89a34ca2cbe0.webp?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Activities and Explorations as a Witch</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate forests, caves, cliffs and lakes on your broom to meet adorable life forms and complete your Encyclopedia.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials to craft problem-solving potions, discover hidden treasures and unlock new paths.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/79d542a97581e8b4dc6574d0459a2e31.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/79d542a97581e8b4dc6574d0459a2e31.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/8431e613dcbd7837f9e20565987c57a8.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/8431e613dcbd7837f9e20565987c57a8.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/8431e613dcbd7837f9e20565987c57a8.mp4?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stories of the Village and Its Inhabitants</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Work as an apprentice witch. Help out at the village and solve problems for the villagers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make friends with the villagers as you restore the village. By establishing bonds, you can unlock their stories and even learn about their secrets.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/157c168581e9778857d5a8ec8c6562ec.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/157c168581e9778857d5a8ec8c6562ec.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/157c168581e9778857d5a8ec8c6562ec.mp4?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collections and Home Decoration</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather recipes and materials to craft furniture, which will give your living space a personal touch.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and customize brooms to add extra enjoyment to your explorations.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/34d1934a8770213d90047cf8c5ade0e9.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/34d1934a8770213d90047cf8c5ade0e9.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/34d1934a8770213d90047cf8c5ade0e9.mp4?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Laid-back Moments</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend your peaceful free time fishing and chatting. Interact with cats to deepen your cross-species friendships.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your exclusive story in this magical yet ever so relatable world!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/9d81b094493e87895bda20d1782bb635.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/9d81b094493e87895bda20d1782bb635.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/9d81b094493e87895bda20d1782bb635.mp4?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/ebd9974420ee4c0f98bdf7e28b2b237b.poster.avif?t=1760421411\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/ebd9974420ee4c0f98bdf7e28b2b237b.webm?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594940/extras/ebd9974420ee4c0f98bdf7e28b2b237b.mp4?t=1760421411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
